{"tid":1348132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急呼籲] 成立人民議會 設立人民自衛軍","createTime":"2019-07-22T07:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T12:48:32.000Z","uid":57614,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"48bbb4d693d62ab4c2b5439d324e76d8c2eee6a8","tid":1348132,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:33:12.000Z","msg":"政府已被警黑架空 政府及立法會無能  <br />\n依家係絕佳時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請文宣準備好宣言 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7df39084d0d7dacc98fa29460252857645486e5","tid":1348132,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:33:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">議會係講未來政制方向，唔會係抗爭大台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係咪連建立新秩序都無需要呀！<br />\n係咪仲要承認共產黨呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jVfqg38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjVfqg38.png&h=55caeed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rMoCSCu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrMoCSCu.png&h=9d632b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3A8vtaQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3A8vtaQ.png&h=b60b0e90&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只要攻入重要建築即可以讀呢篇宣言！！"},{"pid":"9b01a5500d861a8db6ebccfccb9dcbe37b9747fa","tid":1348132,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:34:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"d33b3a0abf17644ba7d9ca6b4f63f9b40226f363","tid":1348132,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7df39084d0d7dacc98fa29460252857645486e5","tid":1348132,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:33:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">議會係講未來政制方向，唔會係抗爭大台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係咪連建立新秩序都無需要呀！<br />\n係咪仲要承認共產黨呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jVfqg38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjVfqg38.png&h=55caeed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rMoCSCu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrMoCSCu.png&h=9d632b11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3A8vtaQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3A8vtaQ.png&h=b60b0e90&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只要攻入重要建築即可以讀呢篇宣言！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:35:45.000Z","msg":"真 首要係要保護大家安全同治安"},{"pid":"4565bdce911ac69dc29442e02ed5b060e2d58919","tid":1348132,"uid":35699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:36:23.000Z","msg":"宣言全文<br />\n<br />\n【721】成立國民議會！香港國民議會宣言！<br />\n<br />\n香港風光如畫，萬物生機盎然，民性祥和平靜，崇尚和平而志氣廣大。惜共產政權接管至今，對國人自由漸施壓迫，先廢我管理市政民生事務之管理權，後再滅我參政為民請命之機會。時至今日更借修訂《逃犯條例》間接斷送香港人人身自由，共產黨惡行罄竹難書，國人有目共睹。<br />\n<br />\n政府行政管治失效，偽立法會慘淪橡皮圖章，司法制度遭共產黨員化，其層層滲透破壞我香港一個多世紀之法治制度，三權崩壞將使香港全域了無生機，國人將因懼怕共產染指而四處逃亡，香港將成空城一座，實在無人願見。<br />\n<br />\n年輕一代以血肉抵擋強權、不惜犧牲以諫國人之決心實在令人動容。吾等眼見香港亂局，有感重建秩序之必要，現於此地建國民議會，廣邀前偽立法會直選議員、有志議政之普羅大眾共議政事，重建我香港昔日之秩序，還我香港祥和繁榮景象，且永遠保護我國人與生俱來的自由。"},{"pid":"675df66716881d5b2e0961b46a5fc40f7da92c4d","tid":1348132,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:36:23.000Z","msg":"要軍火商"},{"pid":"9e0a2e0606c145944fe05fa68cb45aaaa9bdf691","tid":1348132,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:36:35.000Z","msg":"出師表"},{"pid":"de531225fe8c8785e7bd45b4b9e928a44f8f8d24","tid":1348132,"uid":57614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:38:16.000Z","msg":"咁都唔做真係唔使做 一國無制無左 又無政府狀態 大家仲唔做野"},{"pid":"b6c9e4bb77584ceeb42cd04ffeb923cb5d3655b6","tid":1348132,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7df39084d0d7dacc98fa29460252857645486e5","tid":1